Package: henna
Type: Package
Title: A Versatile Visualization Suite
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person('Andrei-Florian', 'Stoica', 
      email='andreistoica@foxmail.com',
     role=c('aut','cre'),
     comment=c(ORCID='0000-0002-5253-0826'))
Description: A visualization suite primarily designed for single-cell
    RNA-sequencing data analysis applications, but adaptable for
    other purposes as well. It introduces novel plots to represent bidimensional
    and frequency data and optimizes some commonly used plotting options
    (e.g., correlation, network, density and alluvial plots) for ease of usage 
    and flexibility.
